column2: select   p.cModelMag_g-p.extinction_g as cModelMag_g,p.cModelMag_r-p.extinction_r as cModelMag_r,p.cModelMag_i-p.extinction_i as cModelMag_i,p.cModelMag_z-p.extinction_z as cModelMag_z    into cModelMag    from  PhotoObjALL as p join SpecObjALL as s    on p.specObjID=s.specObjID join galSpecExtra as e   on i.specObjID=e.specObjID    where s.scienceprimary=#
